author: timesofindia.indiatimes.com
title: Bruce Lee audio launch to be conducted in Hitex
text:
Mega Powerstar Ram Charan, is currently busy shooting for his upcoming action entertainer Bruce Lee. Directed by Srinu Vaitla, this film will celebrate its audio launch on the 2nd of October.
The Hitex grounds in Hyderabad has been selected as the venue for this mega event. Chiranjeevi will be preceding the audio launch as the chief guest which will be attended by huge crowds.
Rakul Preet is cast as the heroine and Megastar Chiranjeevi is playing a cameo in this film which is produced by DVV Danayya.
